        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> November 29, 2025</p>
        
        <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Novalistic.AI LLC ("Company", "we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and protects personal information when providing AI chatbot development, automation systems, and related services ("Services").</p>
        
        <p>By using our Services or accessing our website, you agree to this Privacy Policy.</p>
        
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        
        <p><strong>A. Personal Information</strong><br>
        Name, email address, phone number, business name, job title. Payment information is processed securely by third-party processors and we do not store complete payment card details.</p>
        
        <p><strong>B. Usage & Technical Data</strong><br>
        Chatbot message content (dialog data), IP address, browser type, device identifiers, log files, analytics data, and interaction data from our chatbot systems.</p>
        
        <p><strong>C. Customer Provided Data</strong><br>
        Clients may upload or integrate data into our systems for the purpose of building or operating AI assistants. This may include FAQs, documents, or customer interaction logs.</p>
        
        <p>We do not intentionally collect information from children under 13. Our services are business-facing and not intended for minors.</p>
        
