        <p>We use the collected data to provide, operate, and maintain AI chatbots and automations, train and configure systems to improve performance, troubleshoot and enhance the user experience, communicate with customers, and comply with legal obligations.</p>
        
        <p><strong>We do NOT sell personal data.</strong></p>
        
