        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement technical and organizational measures to protect data, including encryption, access controls, and secure transmission protocols.</p>
        
        <p><strong>No method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure.</strong> You acknowledge that we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
        
